[Name] apmd
[Summary] Set of tools for managing notebook power consumption
[License] GNU General Public License (GPL)
[Description] apmd is a very useful collection of programs. The apmd daemon logs your battery's behaviour and it will send out a warning if you are low on power. The apm command will suspend your system with a shell command and xapm shows the current state of your battery.
[Homepage] http://www.worldvisions.ca/~apenwarr/apmd/
